- Function `stream_claude_thought_process(alert_text, retrieved_runbooks)` that calls `invoke_model_with_response_stream` or `converse_stream` to stream Claude 3.5 Sonnet's reasoning step-by-step.
- Generates JSON thought process chunks (`Observation -> Memory Search -> Action`).

#### [NEW] [main.py](file:///c:/Users/saake/Downloads/sentinel-agent-main/sentinel-agent-main/backend/main.py)
