- Python unit test script `backend/test_backend.py` to verify:
  1. CockroachDB connection & `vector_cosine_similarity_search` / `insert_runbook` functions.
  2. Amazon Bedrock client streaming logic.
  3. WebSocket `/ws/alert` payload delivery & real-time streaming response.

