- Start FastAPI dev server: `uvicorn backend.main:app --reload --port 8000`.
- Connect WebSocket client or test script to `ws://localhost:8000/ws/alert`.
- Send sample system alert payload: `{"alert": "CRITICAL: Connection pool exhausted on auth-service at 18:00 UTC."}`.
- Verify real-time JSON thought process stream over WebSocket.
